But LLMs are not lookup engines.

They are probabilistic sequence simulators.

A prompt doesn’t just ask a question.

It defines:
	•	context
	•	reasoning style
	•	assumptions
	•	structure
	•	tone
	•	constraints

All of that changes the probability distribution over next tokens.

